---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>

  <section class="px-6 md:px-16 py-12 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
      About Gurumantra
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl text-lg mx-auto">
    Gurumantra Center of Learning is where <span class="text-white font-semibold">curiosity meets real-world AI</span>.
    We are not just an institute — we are a learning lab, and an AI Career Accelerator focused on helping students 
    and professionals build, ship, and scale intelligent systems that matter.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-10">The Minds Behind the Mentorship</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        We are a collective of <span class="text-white">architects, engineers, strategists, and founders</span> from the world’s most reputed academic institutions 
        who have spent years building at the intersection of AI and industry. 
        <br/><br/>Our trainers don’t just teach—they lead. With deep 
        expertise across Technology and Engineering, and a strong network across the industry, 
        our mentors translate complex theory into 
        the high-stakes reality of the corporate and the start-up world. 
        <br/><br/>At Gurumantra, you aren't just learning a stack; you are gaining a decade of industry 
        intuition and hard-won experience from professionals who have shaped the systems they now teach.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 md:px-16 py-6 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
    
    <div class="bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-xl">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Our Vision</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">
        To create a generation of <span class="text-white">AI-native professionals, builders, 
            innovators, and leaders</span> who don’t fear disruption — they design it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-xl">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Our Mission</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">
        To demystify AI and make advanced technology
        <span class="text-white">practical, accessible, and career-shaping</span>
        through hands-on learning, real projects, and industry-aligned thinking.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-xl">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Learn → Build → Intern → Launch</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">
        Our approach is simple. Learn and gain expertise, create tangible projects and build a portfolio, 
        work on real world problems as an intern, and launch yourself as a future ready corporate professional 
        or a start-up founder.
        <!-- <span class="text-white">/span> -->
      </p>
    </div>

  </section>

</Layout>